## ClientApp (React error-monitor UI, shared between WebRssFeed and WebApiFeed) - Vite build
## output lands in each host's own wwwroot (see vite.config.ts's OUT_DIR), so wwwroot is
## generated, not source, same as bin/obj. (Already-tracked wwwroot files from before this rule
## covered these paths stay tracked regardless - this only affects new/untracked ones.)
src/WebRssFeed/wwwroot/
src/WebApiFeed/wwwroot/
src/ClientApp/node_modules/

